# Octoprint on Ubuntu

ihar
Ubuntu 22.04.2 LTS
2023-07

## Camera, timelapse

$ sudo apt-get install ustreamer

$ ustreamer --device=/dev/video1 --host=0.0.0.0 --port=8000

## Octoprint

$ sudo apt-get install python3-dev

$ python3 -m venv OctoPrint
$ OctoPrint/bin/pip3 install OctoPrint

$ ./OctoPrint/bin/octoprint serve

